{"tid":631635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：個人反對終身統治","createTime":"2018-04-16T15:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T02:49:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"496f8903594e236e3d1999d62a192944ee1ea16b","tid":631635,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》周一（16日）引述消息，指國家主席習近平在近日一次與外國使節會面上，主動表示「個人反對終身統治」，認為修憲可有效協調黨、政、軍三權工作，又稱在華外國觀察員「曲解」修憲原意。《金融時報》指，習近平主動提及相關議題，令在場人士感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n十三屆全國人大一次會議上月閉幕，會議以2958贊成，高票通過憲法修正案草案，其中包括將「習近平新時期中國特色社會主義思想」寫入憲法、各級監察委成為國家權力部門，以及刪除國家主席、國家副主席的兩屆任期限制。"},{"pid":"67913e113095500b4d5126f982c331a64c0c1640","tid":631635,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180416/s00004/1523887941120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180416%2Fs00004%2F1523887941120&d=I72V8AtZztMkIY0Z8oawy7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=57ce854f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180416%2Fs00004%2F1523887941120&h=d4272509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180416/s00004/1523887941120</a>"},{"pid":"00b0ca53a4f4103847330f70384ad22c0525ea56","tid":631635,"uid":67346,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係當年毛澤東同人講最憎人搞偶像崇拜"},{"pid":"b27c7aabd7a1255451bb1c7ffeb2a1296cd9b10a","tid":631635,"uid":63669,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"朕個人都反對終身制但因為下屬同全國都支持朕登基所以寡人只好順應民意"},{"pid":"2e155739238b5d313377954d2b4b621edbf46c21","tid":631635,"uid":25916,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":